title: Counter-Strike 1.6 by PrivateMS.ru
description:
Developer: Valve Corporation
Publisher: Valve Corporation
Year: 2013
Language: Russian

Features:
Russian interface.
The ability to add servers in the "Favorites".
Work search servers tab "Internet."
Bots. Added by pressing the button of English "H".
Protection from the menu changes and avtokonnekta.
The latest version of the game (48 protocol).
Have all the official and most popular card.
Configuration is optimized for a stable connection and comfortable shooting.
Assembly based on the official game distribution.
Net assembly, nothing unnecessary added and nothing removed. As with the licensed version of the game (Steam).

System requirements:
CPU 800 MHz.
128 MB of RAM
32 MB video card
Windows XP, Vista,
